      "description": "Vault Tasks 0.9.0 is the first public beta release.\n\nHighlights:\n- Global task view grouped by note and optional section headings\n- Pending, completed, all, and section filters\n- Pinned notes with manual ordering\n- Source-aware task updates that write back to the original note\n- Note-level defer and hide controls via frontmatter\n- Settings for scope, sorting, defaults, and task status behavior",
